resources.string:
Velkommen i AA AIO Tweaker
 Denne app vil lade dig anvende nogle tweaks til Android Auto
 Vælg blot hvad tweak du ønsker at anvende :)
 Hvis du er usikker på, hvad en tweak gør, langt tryk på det og en tutorial vil dukke op.

Denne app kan ændre Android Auto adfærd og omgå nogle sikkerhedsfunktioner, som Google har implementeret i Android Auto.\n Ved at bruge denne software accepterer du, at DIN og KUN DIG, alene er ansvarlige for eventuelle konsekvenser, der kan føre til ændringer af sikkerhedselementer, såsom skader på dig selv og/eller andre skader på ejendom, tab af liv.\n Under ingen omstændigheder er forfatteren af denne app ansvarlig for dens anvendelse

Status Legend:
 GREEN= Patch anvendt
 YELLOW= Genstart er nødvendig for at anvende patch
 RED= Patch anvendes ikke

Denne tweak vil gøre Android Auto tror, at bilen er på 0 hastighed. Som et resultat, Android Auto vil altid vise forhåndsvisning af meddelelser. This tweak does not apply to keyboard or first configuration of Android Auto. (Automatic Copy).
Denne tweak vil tilsidesætte grænsen på 6 tryk på Android Auto og vil gøre ubegrænset browsing af indhold altid muligt.

Denne tweak vil låse op for den nye Assistent Genveje funktion. Når aktiveret, kan du gå i Android Auto indstillinger, og i afsnittet Tilpas launcher kan du begynde at tilføje genveje til Google Assistant kommandoer

Denne tweak vil tilsidesætte standardadfærden i Android Automatisk åbning af en navigationsapp ved start og vil gøre Android Auto starte på launcher.\n I nogle tilfælde vil denne tweak deaktivere automatisk start af musik. En kendt løsning er at deaktivere og genaktivere indstillingen i Android Auto indstillinger.\n DET IKKE BEVARES TIL AT SØGE EN SPECIFIK APP TIL AT START FØRST.
Denne tweak vil tvinge Android Auto i widescreen tilstand.
Denne tweak vil tvinge Android Auto i ingen widescreen tilstand.
This tweak enables the possibility to set whether Android Auto must read the incoming messages or not. Android Auto 8.3 or superior is required.
Denne tweak vil gøre statuslinjen altid sort.
Denne tweak vil forhindre batteri-ikonet med den røde omrids når batteribesparelse er tændt.
Denne tweak lader dig indstille en brugerdefineret varighed for hoveder op meddelelser
Denne tweak lader dig indstille en brugerdefineret varighed for medier meddelelser i navigationsbjælken til op til 15 minutter.
Denne tweak bør forhindre Bluetooth i at tænde, når Android Auto er tilsluttet. Denne tweak virker ikke, hvis Bluetooth allerede er tændt.

Denne tweak vil gøre det muligt for tredjeparts-apps lavet specifikt med Android Auto brugerdefinerede SDK til at arbejde på Android Auto.\n Hvis du er bekendt med AA Phenotype Patcher, denne tweak er stort set identisk med det.\n Det er ikke muligt at tilføje bare enhver app til Android Auto, men det er muligt at lappe sideloaded apps MADE TIL ANDROID AUTO til at arbejde i biler.

Dette er en skjult funktion inde i Android Auto-, der vil slå den anden plads i widescreen tilstand til en reel anden skærm, der er helt taget af en seond aktivitet. Google Maps vil vise et fuldt kort med navigationsstatus, musik og telefoner vil tage det fulde rum.
 Denne tilstand aktiverer desuden en anden funktion, der vil slå telefonens skærm til i et andet display for navigation i Android Auto.
 Indstillinger for tweaking af denne funktion vil være tilgængelige i Android Autostartskærm.
 Tilsyneladende understøtter kun Google Maps i øjeblikket denne tilstand.
 Denne funktion er sandsynligvis under udvikling og kunne potentielt ikke fungere efter hensigten.
 Android Auto 5.8 eller overlegen er påkrævet.
Denne tweak vil forhindre Android Auto i at give popup advarsler, når batterisparetilstand er tændt
Tving widescreen er blevet deaktiveret automatisk
Gennemtving deaktivere widescreen er automatisk deaktiveret

This tweak will activate the new built in wallpaper changer in Android Auto. Android Auto 5.8 or superior is required.\nWARNING: If you are a user of Wallpapers For Android Auto, you will need to update it to at least version 3.0, otherwise this tweak will break Wallpapers For Android Auto functionality.

Starting from December 2020, Google reverted a behaviour that happened since Android 10. Previously, the light/dark mode on Android Auto followed the light/dark mode on the phone and vice versa. This meant that switching the phone to dark mode had effect on the car, or if the phone was in dark mode and the car had lights off it used to switch on the light theme on the phone.\n However, since this feature of \"independent\" dark mode was introduced, users with Aftermarket headunits have no way to switch to dark mode anymore without actually wiring the stereo to the car\'s lights.\n This tweak makes sure that night mode is again dependent from phone and switching light/dark mode on phone will have its effects on cars too.

It\'s no mystery that Google logs a lot of data about us. This tweak will make so that Google Play Services will stop a lot of tracking and logging activity.\n WARNING: This tweak has not been extensively tested and could potentially break Android Auto. If you find out that this tweak breaks Android Auto, please open an issue on GitHub.
Root access denied. Please allow root access.
Do you want to revert everything? Please manually restart the app after doing so

This tweak will make so that calendar app into Android Auto can show more days than just one. Please note that even increasing the number of days, it\'s still not obviously possible to distinguish which day you are viewing the events of. Android Auto will just show how many events are set in one day and it won\'t show which day it is.

AA AIO TWEAKER could not find any account in Google Play Services database. This can be caused by several different things such as:
 • Device that is mostly not connected to internet
 • Fresh install of the phone
 • Corrupted Google Play Services database
 • Removal of Google account(s) from the phone
 • Cleared datas of Google Play Services

In this scenario, AA AIO TWEAKER will FAIL to work properly. If you recently removed a Google account or cleared Google Play Services datas, please keep the phone connected to internet and let it build the Google Play Services database fully. This might take several hours, in some cases also days.

If you are not in one of the above conditions, please open a issue on GitHub.

This tweak will increase or decrease video bitrate according to the multiplier set (up to 2.0x). Increasing the bitrate (more than 1.0x) will mean that more datas will be streamed to the car and quality of video streaming could be improved in visual quality, however it might cause instability. Decreasing the bitrate (less than 1.0x) will compress the stream to the car and quality will be decreased, but it will result in a more reliable and fast connection.
The command was not successful. Please wait some minutes and try again. If problem is still ongoing, please open a issue on GitHub

This tweak will activate a new (and hidden) redesign that changes how lists can be browsed with letters. Instead of the A-Z button at the top, the button will appear on the scrollbar when there\'s no scroll happening and you won\'t be forced to go to top to browse with letters again.
A link to the log has been created and copied to clipboard
A new version of AA AIO TWEAKER (version %1$s) is available on GitHub. Do you want to download it now?

AA AIO TWEAKER fundet et stort antal (%1$s) af Google-konti, der er gemt i enheden.
Dette kan have en negativ indvirkning på succesen af lappe processen og AA AIO TWEAKER kan mislykkes.
Du kan enten vælge den eller de konti, som du oftest bruger med Google Play-tjenester, til at anvende programrettelsen på bare dem (2 eller mindre anbefales) eller aktivere en eksperimentel tilstand, der skal lappe alle konti.
BEMÆRK at eksperimentelle tilstand kan forårsage nogle nedbrud på telefonen, mens patch kører.
This tweak will activate a new feature that adds some quick shortcuts to Assistant actions on top of home screen.

Vidste du, at du kun kan fjerne alle de parrede biler fra Android Auto og du kan ikke fjerne bare én ad gangen? Denne indstilling vil redde dig, hvis du ønsker at slette en bil fra Android Auto, bare vælge, hvilke biler du ønsker, og det/de vil blive fjernet.
This tweak will activate day/night mode for Coolwalk mode. Looks kind of broken right now and can\'t handle switch very well.

This tweak will activate a new design in Android Auto (codename Coolwalk) that can be toggled in Android Auto\'s settings and that tweaks a bit the appearance on smaller screens. This design features a always on side panel and some different graphics. This feature is in early stage at the moment. Android Auto 6.9 or superior is required.

This tweak will activate a new options in Android Auto settings to manually customize whether Android Auto must be launched as soon as you connect your phone with the car. Android Auto 6.8 or superior is required.
This tweak will enable Assistant Tips on the top of the home screen for most used actions. Android Auto 8.2 or superior is required.
This tweak will enable the possibility to decline an incoming call with SMS (with Google Assistant).
\nThis option will only work with Coolwalk enabled.
Warning! This operation will ERASE ALL THE DATA from the selected app(s). Please make sure you have a backup of the data. Do you want to proceed anyways?
Finally we are gaining a touchable progress bar for what\'s playing on Android Auto. Yes, we can seek through the current track Requires Android Auto 8.3 or superior.

All this tweak does is basically creates a free shortcut on the home page to open a web page. It involves an Easter egg hidden in Android Auto released on 1st of April 2022. Activate \"Developer mode\" in \"Developer settings\" under \"Application mode\". It\'s the only way to have an actual fullscreen app on Android Auto right now. WARNING: Not exitable, use this if you only plan on using this on your car. There\'s no back button either.
"This tweak enables a movable seekbar for media apps."
"This tweak enables material you style for the Android Auto's settings on the phone. This properly works only on Android Auto 8.8> as tested"
Are you absolutely hating Coolwalk? This tweak is for you.
This tweak will force the portrait layout of Android Auto with dashboard on the bottom.
This tweak will override the default scrolling behaviour of Android Auto making so that it doesn\'t stop page by page.
